---

<Layout 
  title="How Fiverr Social Media Managers Can Help Grow Your Brand"
  description="Discover how to find and hire the best social media managers on Fiverr to boost your brand's online presence and engagement."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24">
    <article class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
          How Fiverr Social Media Managers Can Help Grow Your Brand
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">
          <time datetime="2025-01-15">January 15, 2025</time>
          <span class="mx-2">•</span>
          <span>12 min read</span>
        </div>
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162616305-c69b3fa7fbe0?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
          alt="Social Media Marketing Strategy"
          class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Why Social Media Management is Essential for Business Growth</h2>
        <p>
          In today's digital age, having a strong social media presence isn't just an option—it's a necessity for business success. Here's why professional social media management matters:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Build and engage with your target audience</li>
          <li>Increase brand awareness and recognition</li>
          <li>Drive traffic and generate leads</li>
          <li>Provide better customer service</li>
          <li>Stay ahead of competitors in your industry</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose Fiverr for Social Media Management?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {[
            {
              title: "Professional Expertise",
              points: [
                "Experienced managers",
                "Platform specialists",
                "Industry knowledge",
                "Proven results"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Flexible Solutions",
              points: [
                "Customizable packages",
                "Multiple platforms",
                "Scalable services",
                "Budget-friendly"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Quality Content",
              points: [
                "Original creation",
                "Brand consistency",
                "Trending topics",
                "Engagement focus"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Reliable Service",
              points: [
                "Regular reporting",
                "Clear communication",
                "Timely delivery",
                "Support system"
              ]
            }
          ].map(section => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">{section.title}</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {section.points.map(point => (
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">{point}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Top-Rated Social Media Managers on Fiverr</h2>
        <p>
          Here are some of our highest-rated social media professionals who can help grow your brand:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {recommendedManagers.map(manager => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <img 
                src={manager.image} 
                alt={manager.title}
                class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
              />
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-1">★</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">{manager.rating} ({manager.reviews} reviews)</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{manager.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">{manager.description}</p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">
                  {manager.features.map(feature => (
                    <li class="flex items-center mb-1">
                      <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                      {feature}
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
                <p class="text-primary font-semibold">{manager.price}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Delivery: {manager.deliveryTime}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Social Media Management Pricing Guide</h2>
        <p>
          Understanding the different pricing tiers can help you choose the right package for your needs:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {pricingTiers.map(tier => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{tier.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-primary font-bold text-2xl mb-4">{tier.price}</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {tier.features.map(feature => (
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">{feature}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>How to Get Started with Social Media Management on Fiverr</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8 my-8">
          {orderSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mr-4">{index + 1}</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{step.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">{step.description}</p>
                  <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                    {step.tips.map(tip => (
                      <li class="flex items-center">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400">{tip}</span>
                      </li>
                    ))}
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Pro Tips for Working with Social Media Managers</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Clear Communication:</strong> Provide detailed brand guidelines and expectations.</li>
          <li><strong>Content Approval:</strong> Set up an efficient content approval process.</li>
          <li><strong>Regular Reviews:</strong> Schedule periodic performance reviews and strategy discussions.</li>
          <li><strong>Be Responsive:</strong> Stay engaged with your manager's questions and requests.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Boost Your Social Media Presence?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Browse our curated selection of top-rated social media managers and start growing your brand's online presence. With Fiverr's secure platform and satisfaction guarantee, you're just a few clicks away from professional social media management that delivers results.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="#top-managers" 
            class="inline-block bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Browse Top Managers
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-300;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-white mt-12 mb-6;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-white mt-8 mb-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply my-6;
  }
  .prose li {
    @apply mb-2;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-6;
  }
  .prose table {
    @apply text-gray-300;
  }
</style>